# Windsurf AI Rules

## Project: Claude NextJS Starters

A production-ready Next.js 16 starter kit with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, and shadcn/ui.

## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
|----------|------------|
| Framework | Next.js 16.1.1 (App Router), React 19 |
| Language | TypeScript 5 (strict mode) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 (OKLCH color system) |
| UI | shadcn/ui (New York style), Radix UI |
| Icons | lucide-react |
| Theme | next-themes (dark/light mode) |

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                # shadcn/ui components
│   └── layout/            # Header, Footer, Navigation
├── features/              # Feature-based modules
├── lib/                   # Utilities (cn, constants)
├── types/                 # TypeScript interfaces
└── hooks/                 # Custom hooks
```

## Code Patterns

### Component Pattern (CVA)
```tsx
import { cva } from "class-variance-authority"
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"

const variants = cva("base-styles", {
  variants: { variant: {...}, size: {...} },
  defaultVariants: { variant: "default" }
})

const Component = React.forwardRef<HTMLElement, Props>(
  ({ className, variant, ...props }, ref) => (
    <div ref={ref} className={cn(variants({ variant, className }))} {...props} />
  )
)
```

### Path Aliases
```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"
import type { Feature } from "@/types"
```

### Server vs Client Components
- Default: Server Component (no directive)
- Client: Add `"use client"` for useState, useEffect, event handlers

## Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| Files | kebab-case | `my-component.tsx` |
| Components | PascalCase | `MyComponent` |
| Hooks | camelCase | `useMobile` |
| Types | PascalCase | `NavigationItem` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE | `SITE_CONFIG` |

## Key Files

- `src/lib/constants.ts` - Site configuration
- `src/app/globals.css` - CSS variables, theme
- `components.json` - shadcn/ui config
- `CLAUDE.md` - Full project documentation

## Best Practices

1. Use Server Components by default
2. Keep components small and focused
3. Use cn() for all className merging
4. Define types for all props
5. Follow emoji conventional commits
